ActNational Capital Act
PrecisOrder authorizing the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to engage in an EXCHANGE OF LANDS with the CITY OF OTTAWA involving several pieces of land located near the main Postal Terminal at Riverside Drive and Industrial Avenue, at the National War Memorial (Cenotaph), at the Peacekeeping Monument and along the railway tracks to the west of Abbey Lane.
